name: Findmynumber
0:
”Alexa open find my number”
”Alexa ask find my number for a quickstart”
”Help”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: find my number
des:
If you start the game, Alexa will ask you about the number of players. Then Alexa will imagine a number between 0 and 100.
Successively you can try to guess Alexas number. There Alexa will say, if the called number is under, over or equal the imaginary number.
The first one who find out Alexa number is the winner.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
